These are Puzzles for 7x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, juice, lemonade, mirinda, tea, water
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, helicopter, trike, ship, roller, taxi
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: tulip, sunflower, daffodil, balloon-flower, rose, zinnia, daisy
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, fonseca, chaman, dannemann, bluemaster, dunhill, alhambra
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, drama, epic, horror, martial-arts, scientific, thriller
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, german, malaysian, nigerian, spanish, thai, turkish
7 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish, hamster, horse, snake, turtle
 1. the owner of the frog is the person drinking tea##1
